BEFORE COMPILATION:
Make sure to modify the hiddeninc.inc.default file so it has your paths and passwords.
Then rename the file to hiddeninc.inc

COMPILATION:
make

AFTER COMPILATION:
After you compile everything put the cgi/cgifpcbot file and cgi/html directory into your cgi directory.

Use the file "create_database_script.sql"(view it for instructions, again, change the password to your db one) to create the FB database.

When everything's done just run lfpcbot. It will automagicly connect to FreeNode.
Issue commands by /msg <command> or BotName <command>.